_sText:
Here's my 5th map, I've tried to make it as good as possible. I guess this is also my last map for CSS, next one that I do will be for CS:GO. If you find any bugs, please report them, so I could fix them.

Player limit is 64 people.

It is the first playable build of my map, I will update it and make it better. Don't forget to follow the updates!

**COMMENT PLEASE, I need some criticism!**
